&gt;&gt;Evelyn Rophael: They use
holy oil, and it's a Bishop,

00:52:41.360 --> 00:52:45.740
and they use holy oil, and
the ones they showed you,

00:52:45.740 --> 00:52:48.350
I did two of them in two nights.

00:52:48.350 --> 00:52:52.820
I knew what was involved, and I'd
given each one of them two coats

00:52:52.820 --> 00:52:59.460 position:56%
of varnish, fast-drying varnish, and
as the Bishop was pouring oil on it

00:52:59.460 --> 00:53:01.420
and doing like this,
I'm thinking oh, God,

